vote.title: An ordinance granting a private license to Robbie Drive, Ltd., for the use of approximately 1,600 square feet of land space to install, maintain and utilize a sidewalk café with railing, awning with a premise sign and string lights with four steel tube support posts on a portion of Parkhouse Street right-of-way located near its intersection with Core Street - Revenue: General Fund $1,200.00 annual fee, plus the $200.00 one-time fee and $20.00 ordinance publication fee
